### POST - Crear un nuevo detalle de venta
POST http://localhost:5200/api/SaleDetails
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
X-Actor-Id: 1

{
  "sale_id": 1,
  "medicine_id": 1,
  "quantity": 1,
  "unit_price": 5.00,
  "description": "Lapiz Negro HB"
}

### GET - Obtener todos los detalles de venta
GET http://localhost:5200/api/SaleDetails
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### GET - Obtener un detalle de venta por ID
GET http://localhost:5200/api/SaleDetails/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### GET - Obtener todos los detalles de una venta espec√≠fica
GET http://localhost:5200/api/SaleDetails/sale/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### PUT - Actualizar un detalle de venta
PUT http://localhost:5200/api/SaleDetails/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
X-Actor-Id: 1

{
  "id": 1,
  "sale_id": 1,
  "medicine_id": 1,
  "quantity": 2,
  "unit_price": 5.00,
  "description": "Lapiz Negro HB - Actualizado"
}

### DELETE - Eliminar (soft delete) un detalle de venta
DELETE http://localhost:5200/api/SaleDetails/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
X-Actor-Id: 1
